@startuml
[*] -> Order : Acquire Plane
Order --> Arrival : Delivery Confirmed
Arrival --> Preparation : Plane Arrived
Preparation --> Operations : Ready for Operations, Scheduled Flights
Operations --> Maintenance : No More Scheduled Flights, Maintenance Required
Maintenance --> Preparation : Checked and Serviced, Ready for Operations
Operations --> Maintenance : Plane Condition Requires Maintenance
Preparation --> Operations : Plane Prepared, Ready to Operate
Preparation --> OutOfService : Plane Not Available
Operations --> OutOfService : Plane Permanently Withdrawn from Service
OutOfService --> Removed : Plane No Longer Used
@enduml
